data.description: Historic Dignowity Hill District, Beautifully Restored 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathroom home. With the perfect blend of Modern Conveniences and Vintage Features throughout. The Large Front Porch reminds you of a simpler place and time where friends and neighbors sipped lemonade on a warm spring afternoon. Come inside, you will love the Bay Window, Custom Coffered Ceiling, Brick Fireplace, Open Floor Plan, Upgraded Kitchen Cabinets, Counter-tops, and Original Hardwood Floors. There is an abundance of Natural Light. Covered Parking in the back also perfect for Boat Storage etc... Previously upgraded HVAC, Plumbing & Electrical. Minutes from The Pearl, Fort Sam Houston & Downtown San Antonio Riverwalk.
